page.text: SW BARBUR BLV @ SW CAPITOL HWY/I-5 SB EN
NORTHBOUND VEHICLES TURNING LEFT TO I-5 SB EN GENERALLY HAD TO WAIT UNTIL THE N/S LIGHT TURNED RED TO MAKE THE MOVEMENT. AS MANY AS 6 VEHICLES
WERE TRAPPED IN THE INTERSECTION AFTER RED AND HAD TO TURN WHILE E/W BND VEHICLES IMPATIENTLY AND SIMULTANEOUSLY ENTERED THE INTERSECTION.
